<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 02:14:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“这又发生了”：10 月 7 日失去家人的大屠杀幸存者在议会发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/its-happening-again-holocaust-survivors-who-lost-family-october-7-speak-at-knesset/0000018d-5be6-d4f8-a9df-5feef9620000</link><description>当哈马斯对以色列社区发动残酷袭击时，1,894 名大屠杀幸存者（其中 554 名来自加沙边境附近社区）被撤离家园</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 00:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/its-happening-again-holocaust-survivors-who-lost-family-october-7-speak-at-knesset/0000018d-5be6-d4f8-a9df-5feef9620000</guid></item><item><title>死亡与捐款：10月7日处理死者的志愿者团体是否利用了自己的作用？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/death-and-donations-did-the-volunteer-group-handling-the-october-7-dead-exploit-its-role/0000018d-5a73-d997-adff-df7bdb670000</link><description>哈马斯袭击发生后，扎卡志愿者组织立即开始在以色列南部遭到破坏的社区收集尸体，而以色列国防军则让士兵们在一旁接受搜寻遗体的训练。一项调查揭露了疏忽、错误信息和利用死者作为道具的筹款活动的案例</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/death-and-donations-did-the-volunteer-group-handling-the-october-7-dead-exploit-its-role/0000018d-5a73-d997-adff-df7bdb670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会将投票表决驱逐支持国际法院种族灭绝案的议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-knesset-to-vote-on-expelling-lawmaker-over-support-for-icj-genocide-case/0000018d-5be2-d0fc-a9bd-5fff647f0000</link><description>奥弗·卡西夫否认了他支持哈马斯针对以色列的武装斗争的说法，并补充说针对他的弹劾程序是政治迫害</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-knesset-to-vote-on-expelling-lawmaker-over-support-for-icj-genocide-case/0000018d-5be2-d0fc-a9bd-5fff647f0000</guid></item><item><title>战争已经过去一百多天了，议会仍然没有发挥作用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/over-a-hundred-days-into-the-war-and-the-knesset-still-isnt-functioning/0000018d-5bf2-d0af-a3af-7bfed7db0000</link><description>自10月7日战争爆发以来，以色列议会创下新低，走廊空荡荡，活动非常有限。 “MK们已经不再来了，因为什么也没发生”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 20:58:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/over-a-hundred-days-into-the-war-and-the-knesset-still-isnt-functioning/0000018d-5bf2-d0af-a3af-7bfed7db0000</guid></item><item><title>涉嫌参与杀害巴勒斯坦囚犯的五名以色列狱警被转移到其他牢房</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prison-guards-suspected-of-involvement-in-death-of-palestinian-moved-to-other-unit/0000018d-5bd0-d0fc-a9bd-5fdd88750000</link><description>据以色列监狱管理局称，这些看守因一名巴勒斯坦囚犯的死亡而受到警方讯问，这名囚犯被发现有严重暴力的迹象，并被转移到另一个单位，“直到调查完成”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 20:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prison-guards-suspected-of-involvement-in-death-of-palestinian-moved-to-other-unit/0000018d-5bd0-d0fc-a9bd-5fdd88750000</guid></item><item><title>远离加沙，内塔尼亚胡向媒体发起个人战争，提出尖锐问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-30/ty-article/.highlight/far-from-gaza-netanyahu-wages-his-personal-war-on-press-asking-tough-questions/0000018d-5bba-de55-a99d-fffb01db0000</link><description>来自全国各地的人们正在与哈马斯作战，并被哈马斯杀害，因为内塔尼亚胡派他们去那里。其中一些人确实是记者，他们就臃肿的预算和分担草案的负担提出棘手的问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 20:31:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-30/ty-article/.highlight/far-from-gaza-netanyahu-wages-his-personal-war-on-press-asking-tough-questions/0000018d-5bba-de55-a99d-fffb01db0000</guid></item><item><title>新低：以色列主张让加沙人民挨饿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/a-new-low-the-israelis-advocating-to-starve-the-people-of-gaza/0000018d-5b42-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fc0740000</link><description>对于以色列极端分子来说，在加沙，没有什么是禁止的——阻止人道主义援助的运送、重建犹太人定居点、人类尊严。但将它们视为边缘运动是错误的</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 20:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/a-new-low-the-israelis-advocating-to-starve-the-people-of-gaza/0000018d-5b42-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fc0740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队承认淹没加沙哈马斯隧道以摧毁它们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-admits-to-flooding-hamas-tunnels-in-gaza-in-bid-to-destroy-them/0000018d-5b9e-d0af-a3af-7bbec4750000</link><description>以色列迄今为止否认了外国媒体有关在加沙隧道网络中使用洪水系统的报道，现在承认在“合适”的地点使用了这种方法，并且不影响地下水的使用</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 19:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-admits-to-flooding-hamas-tunnels-in-gaza-in-bid-to-destroy-them/0000018d-5b9e-d0af-a3af-7bbec4750000</guid></item><item><title>报道：加沙停火，以色列人质最早可能下周获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/report-cease-fire-in-gaza-release-of-israeli-hostages-could-happen-as-early-as-next-week/0000018d-5baf-de55-a99d-ffff99bd0000</link><description>伦敦报纸 Al-Araby Al-Jadeed 报道称，哈马斯和以色列可能在几天内达成协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 19:07:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/report-cease-fire-in-gaza-release-of-israeli-hostages-could-happen-as-early-as-next-week/0000018d-5baf-de55-a99d-ffff99bd0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在以色列与哈马斯战争中的新常态：亲巴勒斯坦质问者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bidens-new-normal-amid-the-israel-hamas-war-pro-palestinian-hecklers/0000018d-5b38-d6b0-adcd-7fba045d0000</link><description>随着拜登连任竞选活动进入新阶段，他对以色列加沙战争的支持促使有组织的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者团体在弗吉尼亚州、南卡罗来纳州、伊利诺伊州、华盛顿州、明尼苏达州和战场州密歇根州采取行动。总统正在流失民主党的支持</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 17:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bidens-new-normal-amid-the-israel-hamas-war-pro-palestinian-hecklers/0000018d-5b38-d6b0-adcd-7fba045d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡誓言以色列军队不会离开加沙，数千名恐怖分子不会作为人质协议的一部分被释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-will-not-exit-gaza-thousands-of-terrorists-will-not-be-freed-in-deal/0000018d-5ade-d997-adff-dffe928f0000</link><description>以色列反对派领导人亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，该党将为内塔尼亚胡政府提供“安全网”，以达成协议释放人质，但该党消息人士称，该提议的细节仍不清楚</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 15:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-will-not-exit-gaza-thousands-of-terrorists-will-not-be-freed-in-deal/0000018d-5ade-d997-adff-dffe928f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府新闻办公室接待呼吁轰炸伊朗的福音派领袖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-press-office-hosts-evangelical-leader-who-calls-for-bombing-iran/0000018d-5a7e-d0fc-a9bd-5e7fd6440000</link><description>在一场题为“10 月 7 日战争中的以色列和外国媒体”的活动中，基督教领袖迈克·埃文斯 (Mike Evans) 表示，美国应该攻击哈格岛，因为“伊朗 90% 的原油都存放在那里”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 14:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-press-office-hosts-evangelical-leader-who-calls-for-bombing-iran/0000018d-5a7e-d0fc-a9bd-5e7fd6440000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人表示，该组织收到了在巴黎提出的加沙战争停火建议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/hamas-chief-says-group-received-gaza-war-cease-fire-proposal-put-forward-in-paris/0000018d-5a24-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d9daf0000</link><description>据称，该协议的第一阶段包括释放约 35 名以色列人质，以换取六周的战斗中断，以及从以色列监狱释放数千名巴勒斯坦囚犯</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 14:49:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/hamas-chief-says-group-received-gaza-war-cease-fire-proposal-put-forward-in-paris/0000018d-5a24-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d9daf0000</guid></item><item><title>“必须击败这些怪物”：内塔尼亚胡称加沙战争也为西方而战，回避了10月7日的指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/must-defeat-these-monsters-netanyahu-says-gaza-war-also-battle-for-west-evades-blame/0000018d-5a5f-d997-adff-df7f80000000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在与新保守派作家道格拉斯·默里的谈话中强调，以色列需要在加沙地带“全面战胜”哈马斯，他说“如果野蛮主义在这里获胜，欧洲将是下一个”。美国将是下一个”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 14:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/must-defeat-these-monsters-netanyahu-says-gaza-war-also-battle-for-west-evades-blame/0000018d-5a5f-d997-adff-df7f80000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正走向极右翼与人质家属之间的巷战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-heading-towards-street-battles-between-the-far-right-and-families-of-hostages/0000018d-59c6-d997-adff-ddfe963b0000</link><description>极右翼部长斯莫特里奇和本格维尔有一个共同的目标：将中间派甘茨赶出战时内阁并要求获得席位。现在，一切似乎都朝着对他们有利的方向发展</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-heading-towards-street-battles-between-the-far-right-and-families-of-hostages/0000018d-59c6-d997-adff-ddfe963b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙反乌托邦帐篷城市的生活：“我感觉我失去了一切”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mud-world-gazans-build-a-new-society-in-dystopian-tent-cities/0000018d-5a59-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d50890000</link><description>加沙南部已成为一个巨大的帐篷营地：Fidaa al-Qurshali 博士设立了一个免费诊所，而“塔里克老师”则将他的帐篷变成了教室。尽管严重拥挤和短缺，拉法流离失所的巴勒斯坦人仍勉强度日</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:14:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mud-world-gazans-build-a-new-society-in-dystopian-tent-cities/0000018d-5a59-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d50890000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯摇滚乐队 Bi-2 的以色列成员正在前往以色列的途中，而其他成员在俄罗斯的压力下仍被泰国拘留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/under-russian-pressure-rock-band-bi-2-will-remain-in-arrest-in-thailand/0000018d-5a3f-d6b0-adcd-7ebfb2d40001</link><description>乐队成员担心俄罗斯是他们被捕的幕后黑手，因为他们公开反对乌克兰战争，他们拒绝会见参观他们拘留中心的俄罗斯驻泰国领事，他们的释放被取消</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:39:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/under-russian-pressure-rock-band-bi-2-will-remain-in-arrest-in-thailand/0000018d-5a3f-d6b0-adcd-7ebfb2d40001</guid></item><item><title>他们逃离普京的战争来到以色列。然后不得不第二次逃离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/refugees-again-war-drove-them-out-of-ukraine-then-from-their-homes-in-israel/0000018d-598f-d6b0-adcd-7dbfdf120000</link><description>他们希望在以色列找到一个安全的避难所——结果却不得不再次逃离：“我们意识到无处可返回”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:27:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/refugees-again-war-drove-them-out-of-ukraine-then-from-their-homes-in-israel/0000018d-598f-d6b0-adcd-7dbfdf120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军解雇涉嫌谋杀巴勒斯坦人的以色列定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settler-suspected-of-murdering-palestinians-released-from-idf-service/0000018d-5a07-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f34850000</link><description>Shin Bet 安全部门要求解除 Chaim Pearlman 的预备役职务，他仍然是 1998 年耶路撒冷一系列未侦破的刺伤事件的主要嫌疑人。以色列国防军表示，皮尔曼入伍时并不知道此事</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:13:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settler-suspected-of-murdering-palestinians-released-from-idf-service/0000018d-5a07-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f34850000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处是什么？它服务的巴勒斯坦难民是谁？为什么各国冻结资金？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-unrwa-and-why-are-countries-freezing-their-funding/0000018d-550e-d0fc-a9bd-5f5f45020000</link><description>该联合国机构提供教育、卫生和社会服务，并在战争时期提供救生援助和庇护所，目前是加沙最大的雇主之一。但有关哈马斯参与的指控可能会危及其行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:32:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-unrwa-and-why-are-countries-freezing-their-funding/0000018d-550e-d0fc-a9bd-5f5f45020000</guid></item></channel></rss>